src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130826878.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Saudi Arabia has implemented stringent new penalties, including hefty fines and deportation for foreign residents, for attempting to perform Hajj without an official permit. These measures aim to enhance pilgrim safety and manage overcrowding during the annual pilgrimage, with strict enforcement beginning from Dhu Al Qi'dah.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-tightens-hajj-2026-rules-violators-may-face-sar20000-fine-deportation-and-10-year-entry-ban/articleshow/130826878.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/saudi-arabia-tightens-hajj-2026-rules-violators-may-face-sar20000-fine-deportation-and-10-year-entry-ban/articleshow/130826878.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T16:38:34+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130826831,imgsize-260048.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["If we get deported....": Candace Owens fires back with mockery as Laura Loomer demands probe into husband’s “immigration fraud”]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130816782.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens mocked Laura Loomer after Loomer called for an investigation into George Farmer over alleged immigration fraud tied to a claimed DUI incident. Owens dismissed the accusations with sarcasm, while Loomer escalated the feud by questioning Owens’ finances and credibility. The dispute has grown increasingly personal, with serious allegations still unproven and neither side showing signs of backing down.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/if-we-get-deported-candace-owens-fires-back-with-mockery-as-laura-loomer-demands-probe-into-husbands-immigration-fraud/articleshow/130816782.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/if-we-get-deported-candace-owens-fires-back-with-mockery-as-laura-loomer-demands-probe-into-husbands-immigration-fraud/articleshow/130816782.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T16:32:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130816782,imgsize-39466.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UAE announces long Eid school break as students across Dubai, Abu Dhabi and Sharjah get 9 days off]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130826634.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[UAE schools are merging the Eid Al Adha holidays with the mid-term break. This creates an extended holiday for students and families. Schools are adjusting revision plans and exam schedules. Many students could get up to nine days off. This period is expected to see a travel rush.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-announces-9-day-eid-al-adha-school-break-starting-may-25-for-students-across-private-and-public-schools/articleshow/130826634.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-announces-9-day-eid-al-adha-school-break-starting-may-25-for-students-across-private-and-public-schools/articleshow/130826634.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T16:31:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130826572,imgsize-40014.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Won’t be tolerated’: Starmer warns Iran as UK probes foreign influence amid rising antisemitic attacks]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;ma